      "extra": {
        "message": "No Response Size Limit on Profile Image Download\n\nThe download function reads the entire response with response.read() without any size limit. An attacker could provide a URL pointing to a very large file, causing memory exhaustion on the server.\n\nImpact: Denial of service through memory exhaustion by providing URLs to very large files.\n\nFix: Limit the response size by reading in chunks and enforcing a maximum size, e.g., response.read(MAX_SIZE).",
